ActCanadian High Arctic Research Station Act
PrecisAppointment of SUZANNE KERR of Gatineau, Quebec, to be acting President of the Canadian High Arctic Research Station, to hold office during pleasure on a full-time basis until such time as she is no longer required to act as President.
